  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to have the possibility to use commands and attributes from the Desktop application's menu bar.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Feature\r\n\r\n*Summary*: Implement the menu bar on MacOS.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe user should be able to select options from the menu app that allows her to perform different actions.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nMenu bar is available with very few useful options:\r\n<img width=\"227\" alt=\"captura de pantalla 2018-08-17 a la s 10 11 48 a m\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/44267885-42432400-a206-11e8-98a1-929ad7513477.png\">\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n**Menu proposal**\r\n\r\n-   _[Apple menu]_\r\n- **Status**\r\n-- About Status\r\n-- Check for Updates\r\n-- Hide Status (⌘H)\r\n-- Hide Others (⌥⌘H)\r\n-- Log Out\r\n-- Quit Status (⌘Q)\r\n\r\n- Edit _[only for text editing]_\r\n-- Undo Typing (⌘Z)\r\n-- Redo Typing (⇧⌘Z)\r\n-- Cut (⌘X)\r\n-- Copy (⌘C)\r\n-- Paste (⌘V)\r\n-- Delete (⌫)\r\n-- Select All\r\n\r\n- View\r\n-- Full screen / Exit full screen (⇧⌘F)\r\n\r\n- Chat  _[app specific options]_\r\n-- Start new chat  _[Opens new 1:1 chat screen zpl.io/a7ynPBE]_\r\n-- Join public chat  _[Opens new public chat screen zpl.io/aBE71Xe]_\r\n-- Share contact code  _[Opens user pop-up with contact code zpl.io/bAqjqPO]_\r\n\r\n- Window\r\n-- Minimize (⌘M)\r\n-- Zoom\r\n\r\n- Help\r\n-- [Search box for menu options]\r\n-- FAQs _[link to page]_\r\n\r\n### Visuals\r\n![menu](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37297779/44268547-2a6c9f80-a208-11e8-8733-6dc79acf72cc.png)\r\n \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Operating System: MacOS X\r\n",
